title: Folkal Point-1970s British folk band, 2016 remaster FLAC
description: Here is the only album originally released in 1972 from a group of extremely talented teenagers. Reinterpretations of traditional folk songs set gorgeous vocals and sensitive arrangements. Only 500 or so LPs made it into circulation, and the going price for one these days is over $1000 USD. And for a reason. This is the 2016 remastered re-release on the Forced Exposure label. Includes scans of all artwork
